parameters:
\n[6]: "It can't be helped. For now, let's you and I fight Zaidarg-G
together."
Yui: "Today, I thought... I was going to be done for by Zaidarg-G."

Yui: "But when I thought of you, \n[6], strength just started flowing
out from all over my body."
Yui: "Do you remember what Polka said?"
\n[6]: "The source of the sacred power, is it love...?"
Yui: "The source of the sacred power, it's love."
